OL,4,G1800FPolice Interceptors
OL,5,     GSteve rides to the aid of the
OL,6,     Garmed response team after reports
OL,7,     Gof a man drawing a gun on a pizza
OL,8,     Gdelivery driver. Charley and
OL,9,     GWayne take away a drink driver at
OL,10,     Gthe drive thru.
OL,11,G1900FPolice Interceptors
OL,12,     GSergeant Mick and the Operational
OL,13,     GSupport Unit carry out a raid on
OL,14,     Ga house with suspected drug
OL,15,     Gactivity.
OL,16,G2000FMotorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,17,     FSpeeders
OL,18,     GA child is knocked off his bike -
OL,19,     Gbut the wait time for an
OL,20,     Gambulance is three hours. Martain
OL,21,     Gspots a speedy driver. It turns
OL,22,     Gout to be a takeaway 'emergency'.
