OL,4,G0000FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GCraig's brother Brent borrows a
OL,6,     Glogging machine, leading to a
OL,7,     Grisky mountainside recovery;
OL,8,     Gveteran log hauler Dan Millar
OL,9,     Gbattles rough roads and torn up
OL,10,     Gtires to make it to the mill.
OL,11,G0105FOutback Truckers
OL,12,     GOver the last three days, Steve
OL,13,     GGrahame has hauled 130 tonnes of
OL,14,     Gfreight a massive 2000 km, and
OL,15,     Ghis truck's taken a beating.
OL,16,     GUnder the bonnet the news isn't
OL,17,     Ggood.
